'''Ogami Shrine (Tonami City)''' is a shrine in the Engishiki Jinmyōchō. It is located in [[Etchū Province]].
== Shikinaisha (式内社) == {| class="wikitable sortable" ! District !! Name !! Funding&nbsp;category !! Rank !! Notes !! Same&nbsp;as !! Co-ords !! Shrine&nbsp;DB |- | {{ill|Tonami district|ja|礪波郡|zh|礪波郡|WD=Q11588138}} || {{ill|Ogami Shrine (Tonami City)|ja|雄神神社 (砺波市)|WD=Q11659237}} || {{ill|Kokuhei-sha (Engishiki Jinmyocho)|WD=Q135160342|lt=Kokuhei}} || {{ill|Shikinai Shosha|WD=Q134917287}} || — || — || {{coord|36.591501|136.997058|display=inline}} || [https://jmapps.ne.jp/kokugakuin/det.html?data_id=182391 DB] |}
